            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>新門(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5432:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5432\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5432-TW</a>)近5分K漲速3.31%，21日10:49報140.5元，成交84張，今日漲幅為1.08％。（註：漲跌速為5分K的漲跌幅）</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>新門(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5432:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5432\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5432-TW</a>)近5日股價下跌3.47%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+55 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+55 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：0 張</li> <li>融資增減：-26 張</li> <li>融券增減：+7 張</li> </ul></section><!--$--><!--/$--></main>",
